    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing several species of trees native to the New World tropics, having very hard wood and resin that is obtained from the wood by distillation; used to treat respiratory disorders.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
